\begin_layout Title
Overriding Equalizer Event handling
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Override the Equalizer event handling with OIS event handling.
 OIS creates it's own X Displays for getting the events.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Problem: Remove the event handling system
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Solution:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Override All System Pipe and System Window initEventHandling and exitEventHandli
ng functions (six of them all together) also override the eq::Pipe::createMessag
ePump function
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Remember to override all the functions, for example overriding initEventHandling
 in Pipe and NOT in Window will cause the application to segfault when System
 Window is created.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
