\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Solution:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
XSelectInput(xDisp, xWin, NoEventMask) for Equalizer created window and
 display.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Problem: No Mouse events are received by OIS::Mouse
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Somehow the separate display in eq::GLXPipe is getting all MousePressEvents
 even though the event mask is cleared later.
 This caused the OIS::Mouse not to receive any events unless the MousePressEvent
 was removed from the Event Mask.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Solution:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Override eq::GLXWindow::configInitGLXWindow to create a window without MousePres
sEventMask (also removed all Mouse and Keyboard events).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This solution seems to fix the KeyReceived problem also.
\end_layout

